      A few steps for even more convenient travel
   


   
      Check-in:



      Use our online check-in before you travel. This will save you time at the airport and means you can also go directly to the security check or baggage drop-off. You can check in via our website or app as early as 72 hours before departure. If you would prefer to pick up your boarding pass at the airport, that’s no problem. To do this, come to our check-in desks 2 hours before departure. You will just need to show your confirmation and have IDs for all passengers ready. This may incur additional fees e.g. for a flight on a BASIC fare.

   


   
           
